- Cumulative net gain refers to the running total of net gains (or losses) for each bettor over time;
- Team performance is measured by games won and lost, which are tracked across multiple seasons;
- Prediction accuracy is determined by comparing predicted winners with actual game outcomes.

sql:
SELECT MAX(games_won) AS max_games_won
FROM game_won_lost
WHERE season_id = 1;
